{"tid":1718481,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[喂喂喂]一齊入黎討論下噴巴士既問題","createTime":"2019-11-14T00:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T00:53:38.000Z","uid":4363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"edea853820d537956e5bcb33e06c509e955462ba","tid":1718481,"uid":4363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:44:51.000Z","msg":"其實巴士係唔係真係金身唔搞得<br />\n有幾個point <br />\n一直無放既cctv (係咪真係無放出黎)<br />\n出去集會隨時停(而家仲會唔會有市區大型集會 可能有eg聖誕 除夕)<br />\n一直幫示威者同企係呢邊<br />\n半戰友黎<br />\n<br />\n因為其實呢刻示威者都有難處<br />\nRb有廢老幫手清 rb壽命變得好短<br />\n塞鐵容易塞車難<br />\n如果噴埋巴士就接緊100%整停交通<br />\n<br />\n當然亦有解決辦法<br />\n就係用半永久rb<br />\n鑽埋入地 又或者落石屎<br />\n咁廢老就唔係咁易清<br />\n但手足就要多啲時間搞<br />\n<br />\n真心唔希望大家擺低一句就算<br />\n要只暴制亂就要好好分析形勢<br />\n示威者點先會贏 點先會輸 <br />\n我地都要好好分析<br />\n唔好比佢地得呈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec2134941b79612b3209fab9b8ff41980b31150","tid":1718481,"uid":5276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:45:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2a05d4d3960c0f5a240463c63760413d4bc0a7","tid":1718481,"uid":23672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:47:21.000Z","msg":"頂盡係噴<br />\n唔好打爛<br />\n更加唔好燒"},{"pid":"b0267422fafe2669b3dfdd1ce3c5db06435edff9","tid":1718481,"uid":301079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb2a05d4d3960c0f5a240463c63760413d4bc0a7","tid":1718481,"uid":23672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:47:21.000Z","msg":"頂盡係噴<br />\n唔好打爛<br />\n更加唔好燒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:50:20.000Z","msg":"非常同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8f583695ee79804ae9c747240768b308acccd7","tid":1718481,"uid":4363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:53:11.000Z","msg":"因為見有人話噴都唔噴得<br />\n所以想知大家點睇"},{"pid":"7e876559a0c028291b78d55532f0ebb98272a9b9","tid":1718481,"uid":93350,"like":0